name: Rocket League: Back to the Future
name_original: Rocket League: Back to the Future
description:
Rocket League: Back to the Future is a sports, racing and arcade game developed by Psyonix. It came out on 21-10-2015. Psyonix published the game. The game is rated as "Exceptional" on RAWG.
Rocket League: Back to the Future is available on PC.
